        "# MINI PROJECT : Student Data Explorer\n",
        "# Objective:\n",
        "\n",
        "Create a Student Performance Explorer using Pandas and Pythin to analyze student data and generate a detailed report.\n",
        "\n",
        "# Dataset Columns:\n",
